496
00:38:06,375 --> 00:38:07,500
Tokyo.

497
00:38:08,083 --> 00:38:10,833
<i>Mereka dah keluar dari persembunyian.</i>
<i>Tunggu isyarat saya.</i>

498
00:38:26,291 --> 00:38:27,541
Belum lagi.

499
00:38:34,500 --> 00:38:35,958
- Sekarang!
- Sekarang!

