"Saya ada ramai kawan?"

530
00:41:18,458 --> 00:41:19,583
Jadi?

531
00:41:20,416 --> 00:41:23,500
Kawan tak perlu ramai,
tapi kawan perlu dihargai.

532
00:41:25,500 --> 00:41:29,416
