536
00:41:45,583 --> 00:41:48,208
Ke jerumun singa
untuk selamatkan kekasih saya.

537
00:41:48,916 --> 00:41:50,000
Biar betul.

538
00:41:51,666 --> 00:41:52,708
Sayang.

539
00:42:06,416 --> 00:42:08,125
Saya percaya akan akhirat.

540
00:42:10,541 --> 00:42:11,458
Sebenarnya,

541
